At Thu, 28 Sep 2006 19:45:50 -0400,
Florin Malita wrote:
> 
> snd_card_file_remove() may free hw->card so we can't dereference
> hw->card->module after that.
> 
> Coverity ID 1420.
> 
> Signed-off-by: Florin Malita <fmalita@gmail.com>
Thanks!  Applied to ALSA tree now.
Takashi
